Forme Change:
When an Oricorio hatches it takes the form of its mother or father if the other parent was a Ditto. Oricorio may change forms by consuming Nectar as an Extended Action. This determines Oricorio's primary type:
Red Nectar: Baille (Fire)
Yellow Nectar: Pom Pom (Electric)
Pink Nectar: Pa'u (Psychic)
Purple Nectar: Sensu (Ghost)
